{"tid":381834,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"疑似小麗老師同大隻仔遊墾丁 裙都濕曬","createTime":"2017-08-31T09:19:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-31T14:45:39.000Z","uid":72009,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e7db3c0fca11a338e983cc1d0c1d7794f29f07f9","tid":381834,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T09:19:37.000Z","msg":"俗語說「職場失意，情場得意」，今年7月被取消立法會議員資格的劉小麗雖失去議席，但似乎另有收穫。東網讀者報料指，在台灣墾丁沙灘見到貌似劉小麗的女子與一名男子在沙灘拖手，兩人似是到沙灘玩樂。小麗疑怕裙子被海水沾濕，一度拉高裙子露出白滑大腿，兩人又一起看相機中的照片，小麗更全程露齒微笑，兩人親暱猶如情侶。東網向劉小麗查詢，惟劉小麗只透露自己身在高雄，其他問題一概不回應。&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170831/photo/bkn-20170831122016216-0831_00822_001_03p.jpg?20170831134156\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170831%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170831122016216-0831_00822_001_03p.jpg%3F20170831134156&h=2fb773e2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />大戰"},{"pid":"458a5c56c37a1505e1b942ce69a7df4dac00a8b3","tid":381834,"uid":89134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T09:20:36.000Z","msg":"條仔條褲好樣衰"},{"pid":"b68d96a2ba1aa8e6b081826f02ccc8581e1df0b5","tid":381834,"uid":55488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T09:22:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f8d2e03b050cf87dcce9fe9c781db434ce885c4f","tid":381834,"uid":3128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T09:23:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>小麗真係好撚好J<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n肉地。<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bb0b44d0d90e1ed50fd58477fd7c9ea7a25cb08","tid":381834,"uid":66448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T09:23:50.000Z","msg":"識食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c241afe923f8a023ef2be6156e4acde13